- Create a file named Dockerfile

- FROM: used to import image from docker hub: https://hub.docker.com/search?type=image
- COPY: copy all files in current directory into the app directory of image
- If we use WORKDIR then we dont need to use /app/app.js in CMD (if we create copy in /app) 
- CMD: to execute a command

- docker build -t [tag name] [. represent current directory]
docker build -t hello-docker .

- To check all images on machine
docker image ls

- docker run tag-name
docker run hello-docker

- pull docker
docker pull viraj1299/hello-docker